library(tidyverse)
library(janitor)

cars <- read_csv("../day_3/car_dekho_details.csv") %>% 
  clean_names() %>% 
  select(-"name")

── Column specification ───────────────────────────────────────
cols(
  name = col_character(),
  year = col_double(),
  selling_price = col_double(),
  km_driven = col_double(),
  fuel = col_character(),
  seller_type = col_character(),
  transmission = col_character(),
  owner = col_character()
)
library(GGally)

ggpairs(cars)

modelyear <- lm(selling_price ~ year, data = cars)
summary(modelyear)
